<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-column {\"id\":\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-03296329\",\"paddingTypeMobile\":\"unlinked\",\"paddingTablet\":20,\"paddingMobile\":20,\"paddingTopTablet\":20,\"paddingTopMobile\":20,\"paddingRightTablet\":20,\"paddingRightMobile\":20,\"paddingBottomTablet\":20,\"paddingBottomMobile\":20,\"paddingLeftTablet\":20,\"paddingLeftMobile\":20,\"marginTablet\":20,\"marginMobile\":20,\"marginTopTablet\":20,\"marginTopMobile\":20,\"marginRightTablet\":0,\"marginRightMobile\":0,\"marginBottomTablet\":20,\"marginBottomMobile\":0,\"marginLeftTablet\":0,\"marginLeftMobile\":0,\"columnWidth\":\"20\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\" id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-03296329\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-column --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":32,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2__trashed/pexels-photo-703009/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/pexels-photo-703009-1024x683.jpeg\" alt=\"Tired Man Picture\" class=\"wp-image-32\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-heading {\"id\":\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-f5608b4b\",\"tag\":\"h4\",\"alignMobile\":\"center\",\"headingColor\":\"#d7393e\",\"paddingTablet\":0,\"paddingMobile\":0,\"paddingTopTablet\":0,\"paddingTopMobile\":0,\"paddingRightTablet\":0,\"paddingRightMobile\":0,\"paddingBottomTablet\":0,\"paddingBottomMobile\":0,\"paddingLeftTablet\":0,\"paddingLeftMobile\":0,\"marginTablet\":0,\"marginMobile\":0,\"marginTopTablet\":0,\"marginTopMobile\":0,\"marginBottom\":10,\"marginBottomTablet\":25,\"marginBottomMobile\":5} -->\n<h4 id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-f5608b4b\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-f5608b4b\">SECTION OVERLINE</h4>\n<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-heading {\"id\":\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-e658d9a0\",\"alignMobile\":\"center\",\"headingColor\":\"#1f2025\",\"paddingTablet\":0,\"paddingMobile\":0,\"paddingTopTablet\":0,\"paddingTopMobile\":0,\"paddingRightTablet\":0,\"paddingRightMobile\":0,\"paddingBottomTablet\":0,\"paddingBottomMobile\":0,\"paddingLeftTablet\":0,\"paddingLeftMobile\":0,\"marginTablet\":0,\"marginMobile\":0,\"marginTopTablet\":0,\"marginTopMobile\":0,\"marginBottom\":10,\"marginBottomTablet\":25,\"marginBottomMobile\":5} -->\n<h2 id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-e658d9a0\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-heading-e658d9a0\">Welcome to our Gym</h2>\n<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The vast amount of different and sometimes contradicting information about fitness can certainly be overwhelming, on top of the fact that stepping into a gym can be intimidating for some. Having me as your personal trainer is a great way to reach your goals with trusted methods and will eliminate any fitness or diet related confusion that that you might have.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":218,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/a5213-home/photo-1517837414457-37b44cea4818-1/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/photo-1517837414457-37b44cea4818-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-218\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Welcome to our Gym</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Training with me will certainly have a personal touch. You will have a bespoke training and diet plan specifically tailored towards you and your goals, taking into account current fitness levels and potential injuries. Whether you are reigniting your passion for fitness or new to training, it is important to me that you are enjoying yourself whilst reaching your goals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":228,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/a5213-home/photo-1519317245869-d6943e4a4f9a/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/photo-1519317245869-d6943e4a4f9a-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-228\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a registered nutritionist, I will teach you the fundamentals of a sustainable healthy diet. With me, you will know how to be flexible with your diet, enjoy every meal, and still eat the foods you love to eat whilst achieving your fitness ambitions. As with training, discipline and consistency is key when it comes to your food intake. Remember - you cannot out train a poor diet!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block