lor\">Enjoy Training</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Training with me will certainly have a personal touch. You will have a bespoke training and diet plan specifically tailored towards you and your goals, taking into account current fitness levels and potential injuries. Whether you are reigniting your passion for fitness or new to training, it is important to me that you are enjoying yourself whilst reaching your goals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"color\":\"neve-button-color\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-background has-neve-button-color-background-color has-neve-button-color-color is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":228,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/a5213-home/photo-1519317245869-d6943e4a4f9a/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/photo-1519317245869-d6943e4a4f9a-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-228\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-neve-button-color-color has-text-color\">Eat Right</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a registered nutritionist, I will teach you the fundamentals of a sustainable healthy diet. With me, you will know how to be flexible with your diet, enjoy every meal, and still eat the foods you love to eat whilst achieving your fitness ambitions. As with training, discipline and consistency is key when it comes to your food intake. Remember - you cannot out train a poor diet!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-columns {\"id\":\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-ab67b3ec\",\"columns\":1,\"layout\":\"equal\",\"paddingType\":\"unlinked\",\"paddingTypeMobile\":\"unlinked\",\"paddingTablet\":20,\"paddingMobile\":20,\"paddingTop\":0,\"paddingTopTablet\":20,\"paddingTopMobile\":20,\"paddingRight\":0,\"paddingRightTablet\":20,\"paddingRightMobile\":20,\"paddingBottom\":0,\"paddingBottomTablet\":20,\"paddingBottomMobile\":0,\"paddingLeft\":0,\"paddingLeftTablet\":20,\"paddingLeftMobile\":20,\"marginTablet\":20,\"marginMobile\":20,\"marginTop\":0,\"marginTopTablet\":20,\"marginTopMobile\":20,\"marginBottom\":0,\"marginBottomTablet\":20,\"marginBottomMobile\":0,\"backgroundColor\":\"#d7393e\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns has-1-columns has-desktop-equal-layout has-tablet-equal-layout has-mobile-equal-layout has-default-gap has-vertical-unset\" id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-ab67b3ec\"><div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-overlay\"></div><div class=\"innerblocks-wrap\"><!-- wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-column {\"id\":\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-a9055b78\",\"paddingType\":\"unlinked\",\"paddingTypeMobile\":\"unlinked\",\"paddingTablet\":20,\"paddingMobile\":20,\"paddingTop\":50,\"paddingTopTablet\":20,\"paddingTopMobile\":20,\"paddingRight\":0,\"paddingRightTablet\":20,\"paddingRightMobile\":20,\"paddingBottom\":0,\"paddingBottomTablet\":20,\"paddingBottomMobile\":0,\"paddingLeft\":0,\"paddingLeftTablet\":20,\"paddingLeftMobile\":20,\"marginTablet\":20,\"marginMobile\":20,\"marginTop\":0,\"marginTopTablet\":20,\"m