sonal trainers but me on rubbish diets I didn\'t enjoy, but Mike has really gone the extra mile to give me recipes that I really really love, people can\'t believe how good my food tastes and how good it is for me!','Matt believed in me','','publish','open','closed','','matt-believed-in-me','','','2020-10-28 02:25:26','2020-10-28 02:25:26','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=wpm-testimonial&#038;p=337',2,'wpm-testimonial','',0),(338,1,'2020-10-28 02:26:28','2020-10-28 02:26:28','The gym and myself has never been a match made in heaven. However, in August of 2017 I signed up and tried my luck - alone. After weeks of trying to get back into the swing of things I can admit, my solo mission had failed. Then luckily, I was recommended Mike by a close friend. Mike was a truly fantastic motivator. Even though I leave every session with my legs burning or arms throbbing - I always looked forward to the next!','Forever thankful to the guy!','','publish','open','closed','','forever-thankful-to-the-guy','','','2020-10-28 02:26:28','2020-10-28 02:26:28','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=wpm-testimonial&#038;p=338',1,'wpm-testimonial','',0),(339,1,'2020-10-28 02:28:31','2020-10-28 02:28:31','<!-- wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-columns {\"id\":\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns-f7bf6fce\",\"columns\":1,\"layout\":\"equal\",\"paddingType\":\"unlinked\",\"paddingTop\":100,\"paddingBottom\":100,\"marginTop\":0,\"marginTopMobile\":0,\"marginBottom\":0,\"marginBottomMobile\":0,\"columnsWidth\":1100,\"horizontalAlign\":\"center\",\"backgroundType\":\"image\",\"backgroundImageID\":107,\"backgroundImageURL\":\"https://s33834.pcdn.co/neve-fitness-gb/wp-content/uploads/sites/444/2019/07/neve-gym-demo-18.jpg\",\"backgroundPosition\":\"top center\",\"backgroundRepeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"backgroundSize\":\"cover\",\"backgroundOverlayColor\":\"#1f1f20\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-columns has-1-columns has-desktop-equal-layout has-tablet-equal-