g -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"white\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-white-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size\">Auckland-Based Personal Trainer</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons aligncenter\"><!-- wp:button {\"backgroundColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"textColor\":\"white\",\"className\":\"is-style-secondary\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-secondary\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-neve-button-color-background-color has-text-color has-background\" href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/about/\">Find out more</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-column -->\n\n<!-- wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-column {\"id\":\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-03296329\",\"paddingTypeMobile\":\"unlinked\",\"paddingTablet\":20,\"paddingMobile\":20,\"paddingTopTablet\":20,\"paddingTopMobile\":20,\"paddingRightTablet\":20,\"paddingRightMobile\":20,\"paddingBottomTablet\":20,\"paddingBottomMobile\":20,\"paddingLeftTablet\":20,\"paddingLeftMobile\":20,\"marginTablet\":20,\"marginMobile\":20,\"marginTopTablet\":20,\"marginTopMobile\":20,\"marginRightTablet\":0,\"marginRightMobile\":0,\"marginBottomTablet\":20,\"marginBottomMobile\":0,\"marginLeftTablet\":0,\"marginLeftMobile\":0,\"columnWidth\":\"20\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column\" id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-advanced-column-03296329\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-column --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:themeisle-blocks/advanced-columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":32,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/the-new-umoma-opens-its-doors-2__trashed/pexels-photo-703009/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/pexels-photo-703009-1024x683.jpeg\" alt=\"Tired Man Picture\" class=\"wp-image-32\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"hasCustomCSS\":true} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-neve-button-color-color has-text-color\">Reach Your Goals</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The vast amount of different and sometimes contradicting information about fitness can certainly be overwhelming, on top of the fact that stepping into a gym can be intimidating for some. Having me as your personal trainer is a great way to reach your goals with trusted methods and will eliminate any fitness or diet related confusion that that you might have.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50,\"hasCustomCSS\":true} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"color\":\"neve-button-color\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-background has-neve-button-color-background-color has-neve-button-color-color is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50,\"hasCustomCSS\":true} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":218,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/a5213-home/photo-1517837414457-37b44cea4818-1/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/photo-1517837414457-37b44cea4818-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-218\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-neve-button-color-color has-text-color\">Enjoy Training</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Training with me will certainly have a personal touch. You will have a bespoke training and diet plan specifically tailored towards you and your goals, taking into account current fitness levels and potential injuries. Whether you are reigniting your passion for fitness or new to training, it is important to me that you are enjoying yourself whilst reaching your goals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"color\":\"neve-button-color\",\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-background has-neve-button-color-background-color has-neve-button-color-color is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":228,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/wordpress/a5213-home/photo-1519317245869-d6943e4a4f9a/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/photo-1519317245869-d6943e4a4f9a-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-228\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-neve-button-color-color has-text-color\">Eat Right</h2>\n<!